# contains: true/false membership.
*contains(xs as Vec of i64, t as i64) returns bool
    i is 0
    while i < xs.length
        if xs.get(i) equals t
            return true
        i is i + 1
    false

*main
    xs is vec()
    xs.push(11)
    xs.push(13)
    xs.push(17)
    log contains(xs, 13)
    log contains(xs, 14)
